title: Live NRL trial: Tigers v Cowboys
text:
Simona's NRL future in doubt 0:28 Live NRL trial: Wests Tigers v North Queensland Cowboys updates, scores, news, blog February 17, 2017 5:47pm Source: FOX SPORTS ROUND one spots are up for grabs as near full-strength Wests Tigers and North Queensland outfits battle it out in Friday night’s only NRL pre-season trial match. 
Tigers coach Jason Taylor revealed earlier this week that he’s still got at least one outside back position to fill, while he’s yet to settle on the make up of his interchange bench. 
For the Cowboys, the race is on for who will partner Matt Scott in the front row, while a bench utility spot is also up for grabs. 
The game kicks off at 7pm at Campbelltown Sports Stadium. 
Follow all the action in the live blog below!
